nodes.text: As to whether he can be/do all those things you listed; if he is the almighty omnipotent deity that is claimed, then he can be all those things and more. He can be any and all gods ever worshipped and ever will be worshipped. He can be the greatest of the great and most wretched of all (at the same time). And all this before breakfast. It is only the feeble imaginations of mankind that limit him (which isn't that surprising, given that they created him). Smiley
Well now, there you go. . . .RIGHT ON!!
